    "name": {
      "zh": "AN/PEQ-6 集成战术设备",
      "en": "AN/PEQ-6 Integrated Laser Light Module"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "AN/PEQ-6",
      "en": "AN/PEQ-6"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "一款由Insight Technology设计制造，专为美国特种作战司令部与 H&K Mark 23半自动手枪配套使用的激光瞄准模块。该模块左侧配置激光发射器，右侧设有两盏战术手电。激光器具备两种模式：一种产生可见光点，另一种发射红外光束。照明部分上层为矩形白光手电，下层为矩形红外手电，其中红外组件需佩戴夜视仪方可观测。",
      "en": "A laser aiming module (LAM) designed and manufactured by Insight Technology for use by United States Special Operations Command (USSOCOM) with the Heckler & Koch Mark 23 semi-automatic pistol. It consists of a laser projector on the left side of the LAM and two tactical flashlights on the right side. One setting of the laser produces a visible light dot, while the other setting produces infrared (IR) light. The illuminator section has a rectangular white light flashlight on the upper part and a rectangular infrared flashlight on the lower part. The IR elements can only be seen whilst wearing night vision goggles."
    },
